<% content_for :title, "FairPrice — 美股公允價值分析" %>

<div class="max-w-xl mx-auto space-y-6 mt-10">
  <% if flash[:error] || flash.now[:error] %>
    <%= render FairValue::AlertComponent.new(
          message: flash[:error] || flash.now[:error],
          type:    (flash.now[:alert_type] || :error).to_sym
        ) %>
  <% end %>

  <%= render FairValue::SearchBarComponent.new(
        ticker:             @ticker.to_s,
        discount_rate:      @discount_rate.to_f,
        show_discount_rate: true,
        autofocus:          true
      ) %>

  <div class="text-center text-sm text-gray-400 space-y-1">
    <p>輸入美股代號，即可取得深度估值分析報告</p>
    <p class="text-xs">數據來源：Finnhub｜支援 NYSE / NASDAQ 上市股票</p>
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-300">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-gray-100 text-gray-400 text-xs font-mono">
        v20260420
      </span>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
